@startuml question-lifecycle-states
title AKDB Agent-Authoring - Question Lifecycle States (D7)
[*] --> open
open : open question / pending decision; linked question_about_topic
open --> answered : resolve_question(by=adr|spec) [adds question_resolved_by]
open --> wontfix : closed without an answer
answered --> open : reopened (answer superseded)
answered : resolver linked; surfaces as resolved in brief/recall
wontfix --> [*]
answered --> [*]
@enduml
